conditions:-
`1. If length of s2 - s1 != 1 => False (because we are allowed to add only one different char)`
`2. If s2 doesnt contain complete s1 => False (j < 0 but i != 0)`

Perform this lcs for every curr word with its previously added word (By LIS method).

