we can make all elements equal to 7 in minimum moves 
1 and 13 in 6 moves 
3 and 11 in 4 moves 
5 and 9 in 2 moves 

this is an AP upto N numbers. (Here N will be given by n/2) where **a=2**

consider odd n=6 (input)
